---
title: Bacon & Roast Pumpkin Risotto with Toasted Walnuts & Parsley
description: This hearty bowl of risotto works its magic in the oven. With smokey bacon, loads of veggies and cheesy goodness, each bite is
full of deliciousness. Top with golden walnuts for extra crunch, and a squeeze of lemon for a zesty kick!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-roast-pumpkin-risotto-56b4a890.jpg
